{"an4.42:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.42 ","an4.42:0.2":"5. Rohitassavagga ","an4.42:0.3":"Panhabyakaranasutta ","an4.42:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, panhabyakaranani. ","an4.42:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.42:1.3":"Atthi, bhikkhave, panho ekamsabyakaraniyo; ","an4.42:1.4":"atthi, bhikkhave, panho vibhajjabyakaraniyo; ","an4.42:1.5":"atthi, bhikkhave, panho patipucchabyakaraniyo; ","an4.42:1.6":"atthi, bhikkhave, panho thapaniyo. ","an4.42:1.7":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari panhabyakarananiti. ","an4.42:2.1":"Ekamsavacanam ekam, ","an4.42:2.2":"vibhajjavacanaparam; ","an4.42:2.3":"Tatiyam patipuccheyya, ","an4.42:2.4":"catuttham pana thapaye. ","an4.42:3.1":"Yo ca tesam tattha tattha, ","an4.42:3.2":"janati anudhammatam; ","an4.42:3.3":"Catupanhassa kusalo, ","an4.42:3.4":"ahu bhikkhum tathavidham. ","an4.42:4.1":"Durasado duppasaho, ","an4.42:4.2":"gambhiro duppadhamsiyo; ","an4.42:4.3":"Atho atthe anatthe ca, ","an4.42:4.4":"ubhayassa hoti kovido. ","an4.42:5.1":"Anattham parivajjeti, ","an4.42:5.2":"attham ganhati pandito; ","an4.42:5.3":"Atthabhisamaya dhiro, ","an4.42:5.4":"panditoti pavuccati”ti. ","an4.42:5.5":"Dutiyam. "}